<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-74-0529 </DOCNO><TEXT>In this paper, the author covers several topics dealing with financingfor oil, gas or coal. He explains how to determine the type of financingneeded and the finance differences in commodities and the use of proceeds.The types of lenders--public, private, and commercial banks and theirattitudes are discussed. The paper also gives methods for valuing propertiesand a history of the most recent changes in the markets.</TEXT></DOC>